                                <span class="text-[11px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-amber-400 pb-1">Gold</span>
                            {% else %}
                                <span class="text-[18px] font-black tracking-[0.12em] text-slate-400">Gizli</span>
                            {% endif %}
                        </h2>
                        <p class="mt-1.5 pr-2 text-[11px] leading-5 text-slate-400 font-bold">Operasyon fonu, aidat akisi ve reklam butcesi bu panelden yonetilir.</p>
